  },
  {
    question: "How much do glitter tattoos cost for a Los Angeles party?",
    answer:
      "Pricing depends on your event date, location, guest count, service duration, and whether glitter tattoos are booked alone or paired with another service. Submit your details through Plan My Party and Happy Faces LA will review the best setup and send next steps.",
  },
  {
    question: "How do I book glitter tattoos with Happy Faces LA?",
    answer:
      "Submit your event date, city or ZIP, guest count, age range, and requested services through Plan My Party. Happy Faces LA reviews availability, service mix, travel, and setup needs, then follows up with a recommended setup and pricing. No payment is required when you submit your party details — checkout and the Booking Retainer are available only after availability is confirmed.",
